request.description:
Create auth session context after Firebase token verification. Returns profile if user already exists, or indicates the user must complete onboarding.

Request Body:
- Optional: roleType ('CUSTOMER' or 'BARBER'), deprecated and ignored by backend.

Response (New User):
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "New user. Please complete your profile.",
  "data": {
    "isNewUser": true,
    "firebaseUid": "abc123",
    "phoneNumber": "+1234567890"
  }
}

Response (Existing User):
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Login successful",
  "data": {
    "isNewUser": false,
    "user": {...},
    "profile": {...}
  }
}

Complete customer registration with profile photo upload. Creates User and CustomerProfile records.

Required Fields:
- firstName, lastName, phoneNumber, email, gender, dateOfBirth, address, location, photo

Response:
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Customer profile created",
  "data": {
    "user": {...},
    "profile": {...}
  }
}

Complete barber/shop registration. Creates User and Shop records with hashed PIN.

Required Fields:
- shopName, shopOwner, shopCategory, phoneNumber, emailId, upiId, address, location
- numberOfEmployees, yearsOfExperience, availableDays, openTime, closeTime
- pin (4-6 digits), confirmPin (must match pin)

Shop Categories:
- Salon, Beauty Parlour, Barber, Door-Step

Response:
{
  "success": true,
  "message": "Barber profile created",
  "data": {
    "user": {...},
    "shop": {...}
  }
}
